						               													<description>Boris, Bees and Boomerangs is a light-hearted, fast-paced, real-time roll and write game. Every player gets a Boris card and places it on their player sheet. Players simultaneously roll their seven to eight custom dice in real-time and note their results on their player sheets. Players try to surround their Boris with Bees as fast as possible. At the same time, you have to watch out for the other players! They can hurl Boomerangs that destroy parts of your player sheet or even worse, disperse your bees and unleash the wrath of Boris upon you. However, Boomerangs are dangerous and might backfire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is whoever manages to surround Boris with Bees or the last player not killed by their own Boris.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
